<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.345787>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Cambarellus (Pandicambarus) rotatus, n. sp.: A. lateral view of carapace; B, C, D, and E, respectively, mesial, lateral, caudal, cephalic views of terminal end of left gonopod of ♂ I; F & G, respectively, mesial and lateral view of terminal end of left gonopod of ♂ II; H, mesial view of entire ♂ I gonopod; I, epistome; J, ischial hooks on legs II & III; K, dorsal view of carapace; L, ♀ annulus ventralis; M, antennal scale; N, dorsal view of right chela and carpus of ♂ I. (1 A – E, H, J, K & N of holotype ♂ I; 1 L of allotype ♀; 1 F, G, I & M of morphotype ♂ II)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/345787/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.345790>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Comparison of important morphological structures of Cambarellus rotatus, n. sp. and Cambarellus lesliei. A – C, Cambarellus rotatus, n. sp. respectively, gonopods in situ, ventral view, ♂ I gonopod, mesial view, and epistome; D – F, C. lesliei, respectively, gonopods in situ, ventral view, ♂ I gonopod, mesial view, and epistome. (4 A – C of holotype ♂ I)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/345790/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.345788>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Cambarellus (Pandicambarus) rotatus, n. sp.: Holotype, Hale County, AL, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/345788/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.345789>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Cambarellus (Pandicambarus) rotatus, n. sp.: Two color morphs, Hale County, AL." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/345789/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

